abstract: Confidential documents show that the German lender doled out expensive gifts and jobs to win business in the country.
snippet: Confidential documents show that the German lender doled out expensive gifts and jobs to win business in the country.
lead_paragraph: Good Tuesday. This year’s DealBook Summit will feature speakers like Bill Gates, Hillary Clinton, Reed Hastings of Netflix and David Marcus, the head of Facebook’s Libra cryptocurrency project. Apply to attend here.  (Was this email forwarded to you? Sign up here.)

abstract: Confidential documents detail Deutsche Bank’s influence campaign and hiring practices in China. More than 100 relatives of top Communist Party officials got jobs.
snippet: Confidential documents detail Deutsche Bank’s influence campaign and hiring practices in China. More than 100 relatives of top Communist Party officials got jobs.
lead_paragraph: It was a brazen campaign to win business in China by charming and enriching the country’s political elite.

abstract: The city comptroller will ask companies to adopt a version of the N.F.L.’s “Rooney Rule” and consider women and ethnic minorities for C.E.O. and board spots.

abstract: The lawyer had asked that President Trump and Rex Tillerson, then secretary of state, help a client who was accused in a more than $10 billion scheme to thwart sanctions on Iran.
snippet: The lawyer had asked that President Trump and Rex Tillerson, then secretary of state, help a client who was accused in a more than $10 billion scheme to thwart sanctions on Iran.
lead_paragraph: During a contentious Oval Office meeting with President Trump and Secretary of State Rex Tillerson in 2017, Rudolph W. Giuliani pressed for help in securing the release of a jailed client, an Iranian-Turkish gold trader, as part of a potential prisoner swap with Turkey.

abstract: With New York sharply divided over gifted education, some parents point to a school in Harlem as proof that selective schools can be integrated.
snippet: With New York sharply divided over gifted education, some parents point to a school in Harlem as proof that selective schools can be integrated.
lead_paragraph: Every morning, students from each of New York City’s five boroughs pull on red plaid uniforms and head to an unusual school in East Harlem.

abstract: The man I worked for in 1993 is not the man who now lies for Donald Trump.
snippet: The man I worked for in 1993 is not the man who now lies for Donald Trump.
lead_paragraph: On Oct. 8, 1994, my wife Liz Bruder and I were married in City Hall by Mayor Rudolph W. Giuliani. For 25 years, I carried a wallet-size photo of the three of us from that day.
